---
title: Teriyaki Glazed Chicken Burger with sesame wedges and zesty carrot
description: There are many Asian-inspired elements to this Teriyaki chicken dish. The zesty carrot ribbons, sesame-coated wedges and umami flavour all work together to create a unique eating experience that elevates this beyond your average burger.
